OL,3,C15-year-old murderer to lose anonymity
OL,4,Cafter High Court ruling
OL,6,FTwo High Court judges have overturned
OL,7,Fa decision to allow the media to
OL,8,Fidentify a 15-year-old convicted of a
OL,9,Fmurder in Birmingham city centre.
OL,11,FMuhammad Hassam Ali, known as Ali,
OL,12,Fdied in hospital on January 20, hours
OL,13,Fafter he and his friend were followed
OL,14,Fthrough the city by two masked males
OL,15,Fthey did not know, before he was
OL,16,Fstabbed in the chest by one of them as
OL,17,Fthey sat in Victoria Square.
