OL,3,C15-year-old murderer to lose anonymity
OL,4,Cafter High Court ruling
OL,6,FOne youth, who was 15 years old when
OL,7,Fsentenced in November, was detained
OL,8,Ffor life with a minimum term of 13
OL,9,Fyears for the murder.
OL,11,FThe teenager was not named, pending
OL,12,Fhis appeal against the decision. But
OL,13,Fin a ruling published on Friday, two
OL,14,Fjudges at the High Court overturned
OL,15,Fthe decision allowing the media to
OL,16,Fidentify the teenager, meaning he will
OL,17,Fremain anonymous until his 18th
OL,18,Fbirthday.
