OL,3,C15-year-old murderer to lose anonymity
OL,4,Cafter High Court ruling
OL,6,FLord Justice Jeremy Baker and Mr
OL,7,FJustice Jay were previously told that
OL,8,Fthe process of deciding whether to
OL,9,Fname the teenager was "unnecessarily
OL,10,Frushed" and that the original judge
OL,11,Fdid not provide sufficient reasons.
OL,13,FLord Justice Jeremy Baker said in his
OL,14,Fjudgment a bid to lift the anonymity
OL,15,Fwas provided four days before the
OL,16,Fsentencing hearing and was "clearly
OL,17,Fnot made as soon as reasonably
OL,18,Fpracticable".
