OL,3,C15-year-old murderer to lose anonymity
OL,4,Cafter High Court ruling
OL,6,FThe judge said the sentencing judge,
OL,7,FMr Justice Garnham, should have given
OL,8,Fthe defendant and the youth services
OL,9,Fteam more time, adding: "It risked a
OL,10,Fdecision being made without evidence
OL,11,Fwhich it was necessary for the court
OL,12,Fto take into account."
OL,14,FHe continued: "There is a period of
OL,15,Ftwo years up until he reaches his
OL,16,Fmajority which, in terms of the
OL,17,Fdevelopment of a young person,
OL,18,Fespecially one who has had such a
OL,19,Fdifficult upbringing, lacks maturity
OL,20,Fand may have complex needs, is a
OL,21,Fsignificant period of time."
